// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1575 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: fc6ffe26-540f-524d-9f65-2cba76c514fe

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
